results.description: My business and job are based on adventure travel. I lead adventure holidays (mostly walking, hiking and cultural experiences) which puts me in many places around the world to take fantastic images. The challenge is that I am usually working, so taking pictures, though it is my passion, is mostly an afterthought. I take them when I can and have little time to set up a shot, think through a proper setting, or even letting a scene fully develop before I start pointing and shooting. So I take advantage whenever and wherever I can. Hope you find one to like!
